[media] vivi: Kill BUFFER_TIMEOUT macro

Usage of BUFFER_TIMEOUT has gone in 2008 in 78718e5d (V4L/DVB (7492):
vivi: Simplify the vivi driver and avoid deadlocks), but the macro
remains. Say goodbye to it.

